{"tid":254524,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【警嚴打Uber】司機唔開工！全港車費急漲 中半山加成三倍","createTime":"2017-05-23T09:09:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-24T05:44:19.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eabf679ca66d4b504182246ef4b0f90b870574a4","tid":254524,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495519873_c19f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495519873_c19f.jpg&h=85927c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nUber車費急漲，中半山區的車費，最癲更要加成2.9倍！<br />\n<br />\n警方打擊Uber載客，放蛇並拘捕21名Uber司機，涉20男1女，涉嫌非法載客取酬、沒有第三者保險的罪名。<br />\n<br />\n消息公佈後，有開工的Uber司機劇減，令今日以供求衡量的Uber車費急漲，司機版香港地圖「滿江紅」，幾乎所有地區都加成計費，中半山區的車費，最癲更要加成2.9倍！<br />\n<br />\n對此，Uber回應，對於今早警方的行動感到非常失望，並表示全力支持今早被拘捕的21位司機夥伴及其家人，向受影響的司機夥伴提供包括法律支援的一切協助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56730829&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56730829%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=22bba580\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56730829%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=506ab8bd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56730829&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"424eb59b67820e3926b2f631064609c8a0d5b63f","tid":254524,"uid":64325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T09:14:23.000Z","msg":"Sorry 我係唔會搭的士㗎, 叫啲垃圾食自己."},{"pid":"df4225e5d74e96b68ded8a306b8e3dd03554cf40","tid":254524,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:03:59.000Z","msg":"【警嚴打Uber】狠批Uber零支援 司機：以後唔會開工！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495533398_4191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F1495533398_4191.jpg&h=59dd284a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方打擊Uber載客，放蛇並拘捕21名Uber司機，令司機人心惶惶。Uber司機陳先生接受本報訪問時表示，以後唔會再開工。<br />\n<br />\n他指，「唔會開工啦，一來又唔係全職，都係貪玩做兼職，點會為咗個幾千蚊去同佢博？一被法庭入罪，之前都判罰款同停牌一年，我覺得真係唔值囉。我覺得放蛇會愈來愈密&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n另外，他指出，「警方嚴正執法就真係預左，自從法庭有咗裁決，都估計警察會做嘢，因為佢地有法庭判例Backup。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，令他最不滿的是，「我覺得最唔公平嘅係，有事就只係拉司機，點解Uber自己本身就可以置身事外？同埋Uber對司機基本上係零支援，唔少司機都在Whatsapp群組投訴，一間咁嘅公司值唔值得你去賣命幫佢搵錢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56731990&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56731990%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&d=ppZu%2F4t08H3ZVi%2BcUGUaq5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b288fbe6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56731990%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170523&h=d14e2fdc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56731990&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170523</a>"},{"pid":"ef3c2bd9b0bea104571b0e9f3ece844cb34b9c33","tid":254524,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:08:31.000Z","msg":"無 Uber 我寧願 Call Van <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c8c282aa9e86c05da7da8452a01086ae82ae19","tid":254524,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【警嚴打Uber】狠批Uber零支援 司機：以後唔會開工！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170523/large/1495533398_4191.jpg\" data-